the bed.

"Where'd you get the car?" demanded <PERSON>Amory</PERSON> cynically.

"Sacred trust, but don't be a critical goopher or you can't go!"

"I think I'll sleep," <PERSON>Amory</PERSON> said calmly, resettling himself and reaching
